{
  "stem": "26983.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had an uncle still, this [INAUDIBLE] from Bruna who was in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once, one of the members of the Sonderkommando, I think it was through Zuckerman, I think so, his job was that night to use one of the ovens only for documents.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was also one oven where they burned the documents,",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the documents, the passports, and I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me if they could, of course, and there was some value that some rich people had some dollars or other monies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they couldn't take it out or save it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they burned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't take it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was terribly dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me what they have done with people they caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just poured them with benzene and throw them into the pit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people managed-- one of the friends, Rosenbaum was his name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He told me, he was lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could roll somehow, and wasn't burned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he had his lesson.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this Sonderkommando who had this shift at night for burning documents, brought me the photograph of my uncle in the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was astonished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, how did you get it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew-- How did he know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, so first of all, he knew it because he knew so well, he knew me so well, he recognized me, just by chance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said, oh, that is Yehudah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will bring him the photograph from the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From these photograph, I knew only this uncle could have this photograph.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because all other family didn't exist anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I knew that this uncle went there and perished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time I thought also his wife-- but German ways of life and death, his wife, my Aunt [?",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
